<item>
            <title>[LU-18726] Installing lustre-all-dkms 2.16.1 fails</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18726</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When installing &apos;lustre-all-dkms&apos; package from 2.16.1 version, in the post configure, there is an error when installing compiled modules due to wrong specifications from dkms.conf which is produced by lustre/scripts/dkms.mkconf script. In order to solve this issue &apos;dkms.mkconf&apos; script must be modified. The needed patch is attached&lt;/p&gt;</description>
